        "last_activity_date": 1424186862,
        "creation_date": 1424182678,
        "answer_count": 1,
        "title": "How to escape single quote within sql statement which is inside a variable value?",
        "body": "<p>For log4j I have this very simple sql statement:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>log4j.appender.DB.sql=INSERT INTO [LOG].[dbo].[LOGS] VALUES('%m')\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><code>%m<\/code> is a variable which contains the message of the logger. Sometimes this message will also contain <code>'<\/code> in it. For example: <code>User 'Admin' deleted object C333421<\/code>  (rough example)<\/p>\n\n<p>How can I escape it?<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 28563475,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "sql",
            "logging",
            "log4j",
            "escaping"
        ],
        "score": 2,
        "is_answered": true,
        "view_count": 1573
    },
    "question_comments": [],
    "answers": [{
        "owner": {
            "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/YNIOm.jpg?s=256",
            "account_id": 3282070,
            "user_type": "registered",
            "user_id": 2762432,
            "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2762432/steven35",
            "reputation": 4067,
            "display_name": "steven35",
            "accept_rate": 69
        },
        "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
        "score": 1,
        "is_accepted": false,
        "last_activity_date": 1424186862,
        "creation_date": 1424183712,
        "body": "<p>You escape single quotes by using two single quotes. So for example<\/p>\n\n<p><code>User ''Admin'' deleted object C333421<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>You need to change the String in your java code that retrieves the message.<\/p>\n\n<p>You can use <code>replaceAll<\/code> for this<\/p>\n\n<p><code>message = message.replaceAll(\"'\", \"''\"));<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>Or you could use <code>REPLACE('%m', '''', '''''')<\/code> in the <code>sql<\/code>statement<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 28563820,
        "question_id": 28563475,
        "last_edit_date": 1424186862
    }],
